  "detailed_description": "You know you're a top class Chef, but are you ready to prove it? <br>Show off your Cooking Skills, manage your Resources and Cook in huge Restaurants.<br><br>Host customers from 3 different levels.<br><br>At level 1, manage a dessert shop and bake delicious donuts and cupcakes.<br><br>At level 2, manage a small fastfood shop, serve delicious fries and drinks.<br><br>At level 3, manage a large restaurant, cook burgers, sandwiches, cookies, pizza and much more and prove that your restaurant is the best.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cook A Variety Of Dishes On Three Different Levels.</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865340/extras/9a3970337fe9408bda5dab7f11fbde28.poster.avif?t=1726429495\" width=240 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865340/extras/9a3970337fe9408bda5dab7f11fbde28.webm?t=1726429495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865340/extras/9a3970337fe9408bda5dab7f11fbde28.mp4?t=1726429495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Prepare Great Meals for Your Customers</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865340/extras/ec3c8a750ff959026ba04cb1b18142a2.poster.avif?t=1726429495\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865340/extras/ec3c8a750ff959026ba04cb1b18142a2.webm?t=1726429495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865340/extras/ec3c8a750ff959026ba04cb1b18142a2.mp4?t=1726429495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bake The Best Cookies</h2><br><br><span class=\"